<figureCitation id="13262A6AFFA5FF92FCBCDB7EE102EE42" box="[802,875,1320,1346]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="9.[189,232,1892,1918]" captionTargetBox="[189,1319,768,1849]" captionTargetId="figure-165@9.[189,1398,761,1857]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Fig. 4. A–C. Caponina bochalema sp. nov., ♂, holotype (IAvH-I 3757). A. Left palp, retrolateral view. B. Left palp, ventral view. C. Left palp, prolateral view. – D–F. Caponina huila sp. nov., ♂, holotype (IAvH-I 3761). D. Left palp, retrolateral view. E. Left palp, ventral view. F. Left palp, prolateral view. Scale bars = 1 mm. Abbreviations: see Material and methods." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6468234" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6468234/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="94">4A–C</figureCitation>
